	(31, 59, '<p>EXPERIENCES&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oranizing staff, Atomic Spectrometry and Application Studies, Mahidol University, Bangkok, Thailand, May 21-22, 2007.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Poster presentation on 16th International Conference on Flow Injection Analysis (IC-FIA) including related techniques, Pattaya, Chonburi, Thailand, &ldquo;Availability Assessment of Minor/Trace Minerals in Sediments from Marine Shrimp Ponds by Using Continuous-Flow Sequential Extraction with Inductively Coupled plasma Mass spectrometry (ICP-MS)&rdquo;, April 25-30, 2010.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Conducting research at Department of Chemical Engineering, Faculty of Engineering, Monash University, Melbourne, Australia, &ldquo;Bioactive Paper for Point of Care Application; Gold Nanoparticles Functionalized Thread for SERS Application and Fabrication of Paper-Based Analytical Devices (&micro;PADS) by Low Cost Ink Jet Printing Techniques&rdquo; (Under the supervision of Professor. Dr. Wei Shen) Jan- Sep, 2011.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Poster presentation on European Winter Conferences on Plasma Spectrochemistry 2013, Jagiellonian University in Krakow, Poland, &ldquo;Inductively coupled plasma mass spectrometry (ICP-MS) linked immunoassay using gold nanoparticles (AuNPs) as element tag for chloramphenicol detection&rdquo;, February 9-17, 2013.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reviewer to scientific journals such as &ldquo;Analytical Chemistry&rdquo;, &ldquo;Talanta&rdquo;, &ldquo;Colloids and Surfaces A: Physicochemical and Engineering Aspects&rdquo;, &ldquo;Journal of Hazardous Materials&rsquo;&rsquo;, Spectrochimica Acta Part A: Molecular and Biomolecular Spectroscopy&rdquo;, &ldquo; Cellulose&rdquo; , &ldquo;Sensors &amp; Actuators: B. Chemical&rdquo; , &ldquo;ACS Sensors&rdquo;, &ldquo;ACS Omega&rdquo;, &ldquo;ACS Sustainable Chemistry &amp; Engineering&rdquo;, &ldquo;Analyst&rdquo;, &ldquo;Microchimica Acta&rdquo; , &ldquo;Journal of Chemical Education&rdquo; and &ldquo;Analytical Sciences&rdquo;</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Conducting research at Department of Analytical Chemistry, University of Vienna, Vienna, Austria, &ldquo;QCM and SPR systems for low-cost sensing&rdquo; (Under the supervision of Professor. Dr. Peter A. Lieberzeit) June 1- July 31, 2015.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Poster presentation on Flow Analysis XIII, 2015, Prague, Czech Republic, &ldquo;Chromatic Analysis by Monitoring of Unmodified Silver Nanoparticles Reduction on Microfluidic Paper-Based Analytical Device (&micro;PAD) for Selective Determination of Mercury&rdquo; July 5-10, 2015.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oral presentation on 21st International Conference on Flow Injection Analysis and Related Techniques in Honor of the 80th Birthday of Prof. G. Christian ,2017, St. Petersburg, Russia, &ldquo;Argentometric and Complexometric Titrations Using Thread-Based Analytical Devices&rdquo; 3-8 September 2017.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chairman of academic laboratory competition of National Chemistry Olympiad 2018 :11-15, June 2018, Ubon Ratchathani University</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Internal examiner of curriculum for Bachelor, Master and Ph.D. of Science since 2017</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Invited lecture at 14th International Conference on Flow Analysis (Flow Analysis XIV) &ldquo;Acid-base titration using microfluidic thread-based analytical devices (&mu;TADs)&rdquo;, December 2 - 7, 2018, in Bangkok, Thailand.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Invited lecture at Trace analysis and Biosensor symposium hosting by the Center of Excellence for Trace Analysis and Biosensor (TAB-CoE), Faculty of Science, Prince of Songkhla University, February 10-11, 2020, Prince of Songkla University, Hat Yai, Thailand.</p>\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;&nb